{"lemma":"زُبْدَة","slug":"زُبْدَة","root":"ز.ب.د","root_slug":"ز-ب-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ب-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"زُبْد","root":"زبد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":7,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":13},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17350","n17357","n17358"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8F%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to feed (someone) butter"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to churn (milk)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give (someone) a gift"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make creamy"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to add cream to something"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cause to foam"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"butter"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cinder"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"foam"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"scum"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"liquid"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of زَبَدَ (zabada) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of زُبْدَة (zubda)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17350","headword_ar":"زَبَدَهُ","root":"zbd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (As, S, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, S, A, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabodN","text_ar":"زَبْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fed him with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gave him to eat,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubod","text_ar":"زُبْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh butter"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (As, S, A, Mgh, Msb, K.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabadahu","text_ar":"زَبَدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, S, A, Mgh, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabada lahu","text_ar":"زَبَدَ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, [app. a mistranscription, for its aor. is there mentioned immediately after without the prep.,]) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, S, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) the verb in the sense here following being thus distinguished from that in the sense preceding, (As, Msb,) inf. n. as above, (As, S, Mgh,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave him a gift:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, A, Mgh, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he gave him somewhat, a little, not much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabadotuhu DarobapF","text_ar":"زَبَدْتُهُ ضَرْبَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramoyapF","text_ar":"رَمْيَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I struck him a blow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shot"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cast at him a missile, hastily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though feeding him with a piece of fresh butter. (A, TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabadato siqaA='ahaA","text_ar":"زَبَدَتْ سِقَا=ءَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabada Als~iqaA='a","text_ar":"زَبَدَ السِّقَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n. as above, (A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She agitated her milk-skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he agitated the milk-skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that its butter might come forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until its butter came forth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabadotu Als~awiyqa","text_ar":"زَبَدْتُ السَّوِيقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"added, fresh butter to the meal of parched barley,"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samanotu AlT~aEaAma","text_ar":"سَمَنْتُ الطَّعَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adamotu Alxuboza","text_ar":"اَدَمْتُ الخُبْزَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azobiduhu","text_ar":"اَزْبِدُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) with kesr; (A;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~awiyqa","text_ar":"السَّوِيقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazab~adotu","text_ar":"تَزَبَّدْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA. [Both these phrases are mentioned together, as though to indicate that both signify the same: but Ibr D thinks that the latter means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I swallowed the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swyq","text_ar":"سويق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as one swallows fresh butter:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in my copy of the A, it is written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazab~adati Als~awiyqu","text_ar":"تَزَبَّدَتِ السَّوِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is evidently wrong: perhaps the right reading is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tazab~ada","text_ar":"تَزَبَّدَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~awiyqu","text_ar":"السَّوِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the verb in this phrase, quasi-pass. of that in the former phrase.]"}],"source_refs":["As","S","A","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n17357","headword_ar":"زُبْدَةٌ","root":"zbd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zubodN","text_ar":"زُبْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17358","headword_ar":"زَبَدَةٌ","root":"zbd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zabadN","text_ar":"زَبَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}